ownload PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2534311\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2534311\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 13, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ywt1665702729155.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ywt1665702729155.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ywt1665702729155.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"ywt1665702729155\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      MSS Connector Options\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__mss_connector_options_155244\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">You can assign connector options by setting <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$MSS_PARAMS</span> in the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__topic_d51758e1_d51759e1_d51760e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__p_d51761e1_d51762e1_d51763e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">USYS$MSS_PARAMS</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Option</var>\n            1}</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__topic_d34027e1_d34028e1_d34029e1_d34030e1_d34031e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d786070e74\">\n                        \n Options\n </h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24593e1_d24594e1_d24595e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"iey1665702928398.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iey1665702928398.html\" title=\"Enable or disable testing for the existence of tables and stored procedures.\">checks</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24596e1_d24597e1_d24598e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rov1665702729225.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rov1665702729225.html\" title=\"Determines whether connection pooling is enabled.\">connection pooling</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24599e1_d24600e1_d24601e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"twv1665702729296.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/twv1665702729296.html\" title=\"Set the number of concurrent connections the connector is allowed to maintain.\">connections</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24602e1_d24603e1_d24604e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aci1665702729371.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aci1665702729371.html\" title=\"Specify that called stored procedures should be prefixed with the owner name.\">dbowner</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24605e1_d24606e1_d24607e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vpz1665702944218.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vpz1665702944218.html\" title=\"Specifies the case for table names.\">entity names</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24608e1_d24609e1_d24610e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xti1665702725693.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xti1665702725693.html\" title=\"Specify whether statements remain open after a commit.\">hold statements</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24611e1_d24612e1_d24613e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cqx1665702929661.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cqx1665702929661.html\" title=\"Enable all characters to be used in an object or field, including diacritical signs.\">identifiers</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24614e1_d24615e1_d24616e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lge1665702664169.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lge1665702664169.html\" title=\"Set the cursor type to SQL_CURSOR_KEYSET_DRIVEN to improve performance when using the order by clause on large tables.\">keysetcursor</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24617e1_d24618e1_d24619e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"euf1665702729769.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/euf1665702729769.html\" title=\"Set the amount of data actually locked out for other users when issuing a lock.\">lock granularity</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24620e1_d24621e1_d24622e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ndq1665702929944.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ndq1665702929944.html\" title=\"Set the isolation level for the database transactions of the connector.\">lock isolation</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24623e1_d24624e1_d24625e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fje1665702706365.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fje1665702706365.html\" title=\"Set a time-out period for all transaction and query requests.\">lock timeout</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24626e1_d24627e1_d24628e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mft1665702729839.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mft1665702729839.html\" title=\"Set the number of seconds to wait for a successful logon before yielding.\">logon timeout</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24629e1_d24630e1_d24631e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"vql1665702727392.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/vql1665702727392.html\" title=\"Specify how data types are to be mapped.\">mapping</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24632e1_d24633e1_d24634e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"bvv1665702930308.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bvv1665702930308.html\" title=\"Set the period a database operation will wait for a database lock to be released.\">maxlockwait</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24635e1_d24636e1_d24637e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tch1665702729913.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tch1665702729913.html\" title=\"Specify whether the application is allowed to perform multiple operations on a single connection.\">multiple active result sets</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24638e1_d24639e1_d24640e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"akb1665702945712.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/akb1665702945712.html\" title=\"Enable or disable multibyte character sets.\">nls</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24644e1_d24645e1_d24646e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dbw1665702729981.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dbw1665702729981.html\" title=\"Specify whether physical row addresses (PRAs) are used to identify rows.\">pra</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24647e1_d24648e1_d24649e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jbg1665702730049.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jbg1665702730049.html\" title=\"Specify whether the connector will use stored procedures to update, insert, delete, and fetch data, or use SQL instead.\">procedures</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24650e1_d24651e1_d24652e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gxp1665702946474.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gxp1665702946474.html\" title=\"Specify the maximum record size.\">record size</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24653e1_d24654e1_d24655e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nzb1665702931579.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nzb1665702931579.html\" title=\"Specify whether Uniface or the DBMS is responsible for maintaining referential integrity.\">ri</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24656e1_d24657e1_d24658e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ohd1665702931867.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ohd1665702931867.html\" title=\"Specify whether segmented fields will be stored to large object data types.\">segmented fields</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24659e1_d24660e1_d24661e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ddw1665702730320.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ddw1665702730320.html\" title=\"Specify that Uniface should not remove the cached SELECT statement until the next SELECT statement is different than the previous one.\">slctenhance</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24662e1_d24663e1_d24664e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"spv1665702730389.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/spv1665702730389.html\" title=\"Determines how NULL values are handled in concatenation and aggregate functions.\">sql92npw</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24665e1_d24666e1_d24667e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wdj1665702932289.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wdj1665702932289.html\" title=\"Set the number of rows the connector selects from the DBMS in each step of the Uniface stepped hitlist.\">step size</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24668e1_d24669e1_d24670e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aht1719471196112.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aht1719471196112.html\" title=\"Specify whether Uniface should enable or disable the Uniface cache mechanism for statements.\">stmtcache</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24671e1_d24672e1_d24673e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qql1665702730534.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qql1665702730534.html\" title=\"Specify whether Uniface should use stored procedures when updating BLOB data (SC*)\">updblobspr</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24674e1_d24675e1_d24676e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cgi1665702623680.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cgi1665702623680.html\" title=\"Specify whether the connector will use stored procedures that work with paranoid locking.\">upgrade fetch procedures</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__topic_d34032e1_d34033e1_d34034e1_d34035e1_d34036e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d786070e363\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__d6884e20\">Most connector options enable or disable features. Some options have a numeric parameter (a non negative decimal integer). Every numeric option has a default value, although the range of valid values is option-specific.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__topic_d34037e1_d34038e1_d34039e1_d34040e1_d34041e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d786070e372\">\n                        \n Syntax Rules\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__p_d51776e1_d51777e1_d51778e1\">The syntax rules for <code class=\"ph codeph\">USYS$MSS_PARAMS</code> are:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24677e1_d24678e1_d24679e1\">All options have the form <var class=\"keyword varname\">Directive</var> = <var class=\"keyword varname\">Value</var>. Instead of the equals sign (<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>), a colon (<code class=\"ph codeph\">:</code>) can be used.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24680e1_d24681e1_d24682e1\">The total length of the assignment should not exceed 2048 characters. Use the short format shown in the example for multiple options.\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24683e1_d24684e1_d24685e1\">Each option must be specified only once\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24686e1_d24687e1_d24688e1\">Multiple options must be separated by commas (<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>)\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24689e1_d24690e1_d24691e1\">Words and numbers within each option are separated by one or more spaces or tabs\n </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"ywt1665702729155__li_d24692e1_d24693e1_d24694e1\">Options are not case-dependent\n </li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">Example long format for two options:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">USYS$MSS_PARAMS = isolation=read uncommitted, entity names=upper</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">Example short format for four options:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">USYS$MSS_PARAMS = iso:ru, ents:upper, procs:off, mapping=2</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/msq1665702542189.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>[DRIVER_SETTINGS]</a><p>Use the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file to specify the database and component engine connectors used, and their parameter options. The options available depend on the connector in use.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534311\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534311\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "MSS Connector Options Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 13, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 MSS Connector Options You can assign connector options by setting USYS$MSS_PARAMS in the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file. USYS$MSS_PARAMS Option { , Option 1} Options checks connection pooling connections dbowner entity names hold statements identifiers keysetcursor lock granularity lock isolation lock timeout logon timeout mapping maxlockwait multiple active result sets nls pra procedures record size ri segmented fields slctenhance sql92npw step size stmtcache updblobspr upgrade fetch procedures Description Most connector options enable or disable features. Some options have a numeric parameter (a non negative decimal integer). Every numeric option has a default value, although the range of valid values is option-specific. Syntax Rules The syntax rules for USYS$MSS_PARAMS are: All options have the form Directive = Value . Instead of the equals sign ( = ), a colon ( : ) can be used. The total length of the assignment should not exceed 2048 characters. Use the short format shown in the example for multiple options. Each option must be specified only once Multiple options must be separated by commas ( , ) Words and numbers within each option are separated by one or more spaces or tabs Options are not case-dependent Example long format for two options: USYS$MSS_PARAMS = isolation=read uncommitted, entity names=upper Copy Example short format for four options: USYS$MSS_PARAMS = iso:ru, ents:upper, procs:off, mapping=2 Copy Related Links [DRIVER_SETTINGS] Use the [DRIVER_SETTINGS] section of the assignment file to specify the database and component engine connectors used, and their parameter options. The options available depend on the connector in use. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}